### ARCH-1: RLS Policies Reference `profiles.role` — Disconnected from Multi-Club

All RLS in `01_arkib_rls.sql` and `04_department_and_membership.sql` check `profiles.role` + `profiles.club_id`. In a multi-club system, a CLUB_PRESIDENT in Club A passes the RLS check for Club B's data because `profiles.role` = `CLUB_PRESIDENT` with no actual club membership verification.

> [!WARNING]
> Root cause of cross-club data leakage at the DB level.

